# and /investigate-mismatch — never ship these to GitHub releases or AUR
# tarballs. The pattern catches future variants automatically.
*_REMEDIATION.md
# /audit findings (cross-stack quality reports) — internal-only, not for
# releases or AUR tarballs.
AUDIT_*.md
